  "texts": [
    "Smart technology can help identify these changes and adjust the test to make it more stable and reliable.",
    "Security Vulnerabilities in DevOps ProcessesDevOps also talks about automating different dashboards and alerts, so people monitoring applications in real time can get better intelligence when security occurs.",
    "This is what we've been doing in software for a long time.",
    "I think DevOps is demanding more of it and putting a nice name in front of it, and at least in my world, trying to add more security to it and make it as automated as possible.",
